=== Schema Changes ===
New table: public.intake_submissions
  id uuid PK, tenant_id uuid FK tenants, form_type text CHECK(seller|buyer|birddog),
  payload jsonb, source text, submitted_at timestamptz, reviewed_at timestamptz, created_at timestamptz
  REVOKE ALL from anon/authenticated. RLS USING+WITH CHECK. Index (tenant_id, submitted_at DESC, id DESC).

New table: public.intake_buyers
  id uuid PK, tenant_id uuid FK tenants, name text, email text, phone text,
  areas_of_interest text, budget_range text, deal_type_tags text[], price_range_notes text,
  notes text, is_active boolean, created_at timestamptz, updated_at timestamptz
  REVOKE ALL from anon/authenticated. RLS USING+WITH CHECK. Index (tenant_id, created_at DESC, id DESC).

No existing tables modified.

=== RPCs ===
submit_form_v1(p_slug text, p_form_type text, p_payload jsonb)
  DROP + recreate. All 10.8.11N logic preserved. Now also writes intake_submissions row.
  Return type: jsonb. Subscription query deterministic (ORDER BY created_at DESC LIMIT 1).
  Safe numeric cast via NULLIF. GRANT anon + authenticated.

list_intake_submissions_v1(p_limit int DEFAULT 25)
  New. Authenticated only. Tenant-scoped. Deterministic order (submitted_at DESC, id DESC).
  p_limit validated 1-100.

list_buyers_v1(p_limit int DEFAULT 25)
  New. Authenticated only. Tenant-scoped. Deterministic order (created_at DESC, id DESC).
  p_limit validated 1-100.

